{"tid":2464044,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個婉轉嘅被表白方式","createTime":"2021-03-27T07:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T10:21:21.000Z","uid":307910,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7686b64c06180802359252714f1d69fc45feedaa","tid":2464044,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:「其實你覺得我哋夾唔夾」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:「夾啦緊係，我哋性格一凹一凸咁」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「其實我check過你星座，仲check埋你嘅生日書，我哋個運勢唔係好夾」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「呢啲嘢唔係咁架喎，唔通我喺呢個月生日嘅人就永遠無得同你呢個月生日嘅人一齊咩」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「我之前同過一啲唔啱星座嘅人一齊，去到最後都分咗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「有更加多所謂星座唔同嘅人一齊得好地地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「我唔止同你夾，我亦都會令你好開心」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好啦，我聽日要搭九點機，但我到而家都瞓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「我讀啲嘢氹你瞓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「好呀」<br />\n（讀者咗十分鐘之後傳來鼻鼾聲）<br />\n<br />\n我聽咗佢啲鼻鼾聲三個字，我一世人都未聽過咁好聽嘅鼻鼾聲」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:「依！你仲未收線呀...」、<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「唔捨得收線呀，kellyb」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「口花花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」"},{"pid":"d14c8a08e5ea92cf006e1019c428f47c14b54f96","tid":2464044,"uid":307910,"like":1,"d